```java
public static boolean getLock(String key) {
    Long flag = jedis.setnx(key, "1");
    if (flag == 1) {
        jedis.expire(key, 10);
    }
    return flag == 1;
}

public static void releaseLock(String key) {
    jedis.del(key);
}
```

